<body class="d-flex flex-column vh-100 bg-black">
    <main style="width: min(95%, 35rem); margin-inline: auto;">
        <div class="container-fluid text-center px-3 mt-3">
            <div class="mb-3 pt-3">
                <img src="/images/newlogo.png" style="max-width: 98%; height: auto;">
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="mb-3" style="color: white; align-self: center">Welcome to Hold It!</h4>
                
                <p style="color: white;">What is Hold It? At our core, we're an app designed to track how long a user can hold their breath. We keep track of all your holds and display them along with some relevant stats to help you improve and compete with others.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center;" class="mb-3">
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary fw-bold bg-dark border-0 mx-1" style="min-width: 40%;">Login</a>
                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary fw-bold bg-dark border-0 mx-1" style="min-width: 40%;">Register</a>
            </div>
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center;" class="mb-3">
                <a href="/breathholds" class="btn btn-sm btn-danger fw-bold border-0" style="min-width: 80%;">View Holds</a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p style="color: white;">Looking for tips to help you improve your Holds? Try the Wim Hof Method, we're big fans here at Hold It. Use the links below to find out more about Wim Hof and his methods. Then come back and give them a shot, see how much you improve.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="background-color: #3b3b3b; height: 1px;" class="mb-3"></div>
            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
                <span style="color:white;">Site</span>
                <a href="https://www.wimhofmethod.com/" class="mb-3" style="color: #a1a1a1;">Wim Hof Method</a>
                <span style="color:white;">Video</span>
                <a href="https://youtu.be/IFSL_Qk9qKw" style="color: #a1a1a1;">Safety (3:17)</a>
                <a href="https://youtu.be/IFSL_Qk9qKw" style="color: #a1a1a1;">Tutorial w/Wim Hof (10:17)</a>
                <a href="https://youtu.be/tybOi4hjZFQ" style="color: #a1a1a1;">Guided Session (11:00)</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer class="footer bg-black py-2 mt-auto">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: .8rem;">&copyHOLD IT! 2021</span>
        </div>
    </footer>
